<div tiddler="MonospacedText" modifier="JeremyRuston" modified="200509171808" created="200509171808" tags="formatting">{{{Monospaced text}}} is supported - edit this tiddler to see the syntax.\n\nYou can also have monospaced blocks (useful for source code):\n\n{{{\nvar posTop = findPosY(e);\nvar posBot = posTop + e.offsetHeight;\nvar winTop = findScrollY();\nvar winHeight = findWindowHeight();\nvar winBot = winTop + winHeight;\nif(posTop &lt; winTop)\nreturn(posTop);\nelse if(posBot &gt; winBot)\n{\nif(e.offsetHeight &lt; winHeight)\nreturn(posTop - (winHeight - e.offsetHeight));\nelse\nreturn(posTop);\n}\nelse\nreturn(winTop);\n}}}\n</div>